data.name: MainLabel.Text
data.value:
-> Your goal is to catch as many critters as possible (high score).
-> Butterflies are worth 1 point, mice are worth 2 points, snakes are worth 3 points, and laser pointer dots are worth 5 (those things are fast!)- and if you catch a laser dot, you get to shoot a laser beam three times (use space)!
-> Get 30 points for level 2: faster critters- bats, bugs, and moths!
-> Use the mouse to move.
-> Sometimes, a critter escapes down a hole (cats can't fit down the holes). When 5 critters have escaped, the game is over.
-> Enter your name and press Enter to begin! (Press Escape to quit)
